@startuml

participant 客户企业财务编排服务 as f
participant 企业差旅服务 as t
database 数据库 as db
participant 对公转账系统 as u

f -> t: 1. POST /travel-contracts/{cid}/fixd-fee
t -> db: 2. 保存固定服务费用支付请求
t -> u: 3. POST /union-pay/payments
u --> t
t --> f
u -> : 对接银联对公转账系统
u <-- : 客户完成支付
u -> t: 4. POST /travel-contracts/{cid}/fixd-fee/confirmation
t --> u

@enduml